Rating: 3
This cake is tender and moist, and flavors go well together. I added a little bourbon to the ganache to carry that flavor over. Although I whipped the egg whites on medium speed to allow for expansion in the oven, the cake fell quite a bit after I removed it. So, although the cake was delicious, the presentation suffered.